track_getSimilar(track, artist, mbid = NA, autocorrect = NA, limit = NA)

Arguments

track

The track name.
artist

The artist name.
mbid

The musicbrainz id for the track
autocorrect

limit

Maximum number of similar tracks to return.

A list of the similar tracks.
